      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound BMW E46 M3, a quintessential analog performance machine. At its heart is the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS, delivering a linear power band up to an 8,000 RPM redline. This example features a reinforced rear subframe and a recently refreshed cooling system, addressing key platform vulnerabilities. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers tactile shifts, paired with an M-Variable limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. Suspension is dialed in with poly-bushings and adjustable dampers, ensuring precise turn-in and controlled rebound. While showing minor aesthetic wear and honest patina consistent with its age, the drivetrain remains tight and the engine pulls strongly through every gear. A true driver-spec E46 ready for the canyons.",
